Sentencas: The utilization of identical anode and cathode materials in symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells (SSOFCs) can efficiently reduce their fabrication costs and prolong their operational life.
Titulo: Nb-doped double perovskite Sr2CoFeO6_ δ as an efficient and prospective electrode for quasi-symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Herein, Nb-doped double perovskite Sr2CoFeO6-& delta; of a traditional cathode was employed as the electrode material for SSOFCs.
Titulo: Nb-doped double perovskite Sr2CoFeO6_ δ as an efficient and prospective electrode for quasi-symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Notably, the electrochemical performance and reversibility were improved due to Nb doping.
Titulo: Nb-doped double perovskite Sr2CoFeO6_ δ as an efficient and prospective electrode for quasi-symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The Nb-doped sample Sr2CoFe0.7Nb0.3O6_& delta;.5 (SCFN3) was synthesized in air, which decomposed into Co-Fe alloy, SrCoO2.25, and Sr3FeNbO6_& delta; in H2.
Titulo: Nb-doped double perovskite Sr2CoFeO6_ δ as an efficient and prospective electrode for quasi-symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Following calcination in air, the sample reverted to the original perovskite structure.
Titulo: Nb-doped double perovskite Sr2CoFeO6_ δ as an efficient and prospective electrode for quasi-symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The SCFN3 sample exhibited good chemical compatibility with SOFC electrolytes such as La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.2O3_& delta; (LSGM), Sm0.2Ce0.8O2_& delta;, and BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.1Yb0.1O3_& delta;.
Titulo: Nb-doped double perovskite Sr2CoFeO6_ δ as an efficient and prospective electrode for quasi-symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A single cell consisting of 300-& mu;m LSGM electrolyte exhibited maximum power densities of 951, 510, 563, and 397 mW/cm2 at 850 & DEG;C when using H2, C3H8, liquid C2H5OH, and solid C as fuels, respectively.
Titulo: Nb-doped double perovskite Sr2CoFeO6_ δ as an efficient and prospective electrode for quasi-symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: These findings adequately demonstrate the fuel-flexible characteristics of SOFCs.
Titulo: Nb-doped double perovskite Sr2CoFeO6_ δ as an efficient and prospective electrode for quasi-symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells
